<p>For those not familiar with Wealth-Lab, our <strong>web-based backtestin=
g engine</strong> is free to use. Users can design a trading system in a us=
er-friendly interface and run backtests of your strategy right in the brows=
er. As a natural next step, your strategy will become instantly available i=
n the Wealth-Lab desktop application for in-depth use. And if you find that=
 your strategy works well, you can opt to publish it for the benefit of oth=
er users in the Wealth-Lab community.</p>
<p>This sample strategy based on the SDO indicator can be downloaded from o=
ur =E2=80=9Cpublished strategies=E2=80=9D listing at: <a href=3D"https://ww=
